negative.review:
This is a decent game, but there are some problems that make me not want to recommend it.

Balance: Getting my weapon skills stopped by EVERY F*ING MINOR ATTACK FROM ANY F*ING ENEMY, even tho i'm wearining one of the tankiest loadout i could use, MAKES NO F*ING SENSE! I have to hit the enemies 3+ times for them to stagger for 1s, but anything f*s me over, seriously, what a s*tty a** system;

Maps: The maps in this game are some of the worst i ever saw in any game. Almost all of them have are just a narrow path with pits on both side that are there just to f* u over and kill u for no reason. Cause of that u are almost forced to play with 2-hand sword and block every attack, otherwise u will be killed by gravity more than by enemies;

Block: U have like 3 weapons u can fully block attacks, so u are very limited, and u still get status effects from blocked attacks, which MAKES NO F*ING SENSE!;

Mastering gifts: This system is kinda interesting, till u notice how many classes and skills there are in this game, then it becomes a stupid a** idea and just an annoying af system;

Last boss: Just... a joke... probably the esiest boss in the game, i dont understand why so many devs dont understand the concept of a 'last boss'...;

I bought this game cause of the 2* one that is coming, but after playing this one, i dont care about the 2* anymore ü§Æü§°

